title: Question about factory images for Pixel 4.
content:
I have an unlocked Pixel 4 XL purchased directly from the Google Store and I am using it on the AT&T network.  I'm not sure which factory image to install.  I assume the one for AT&T but I wasn't sure if that was built specifically for Pixel 4 phones that were purchased directly from AT&T.

Which factory image should I install?
Pixel 4 (XL): 
US (ATT & Verizon): QD1A.190821.014.C2
US (TMobile, Sprint, Google Fi) & UK carriers: QD1A.190821.014
All other carriers (AU/JP/CA/TW/US): QD1A.190821.007.A3
